{
  "stem": "15694.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then I decided that in-- well, I guess they had-- half of that went for-- on train fares.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I decided to go all the way by bicycle and save the train-- train fares.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after five weeks, I could buy myself a Diana air rifle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was my little six-year-old sister who hit the-- who hit bull's eye first.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was like in a sort of match, in a game with other boys of my age.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my little sister, six years younger, comes along and hits bullseye first time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was rather proud and--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a fond memory.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyway-- well, what should I tell you next?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Probably sometimes thoughts in-- do-- had-- in due cause of the story, thoughts come, and I have to sort of switch back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But at the moment, I would possibly go straight on to 1938.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In '36.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah. '38, one morning 6-- 6-- 6 o'clock in the morning, the bells went.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The doorbell went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And three men entered.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I thought, gestapo.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they ask, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Get dressed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Come along.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And any questions were not answered.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my-- my father, myself got dressed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother said she didn't feel well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She had to join us later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when we then later met at a station, we were one of the very few people who had still suitcases, because Mother and sister packed them suitcases.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were going to be deported to Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Apparently Poland at that time let it be known that whoever holds a Polish passport and hasn't been to Poland for a certain amount-- number of years will lose Polish--",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--citizenship, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Germans took this as a pretense, and gathered all those with Polish passports and put them through the border.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
